com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport

Enum SortType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SortType>
      • com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport.SortType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SortType>

    public enum SortType
extends Enum<SortType>
    Indicates what aspect of Items is used as the basis for a sort operation.
    Since:
    2.0

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CREATED_TIMESTAMP
      The Items will be sorted according to when they were created.
      MODIFIED_TIMESTAMP
      The Items will be sorted according to when they were last modified.
      NATURAL_ORDER
      The Items will be sorted according to a reproducible scheme defined by the system.
      PROPERTY_TYPE
      The Items will be sorted according to their first value for a (specified) PropertyType.
      SCORE
      The Items will be sorted according to their score.
